</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB63960574DFFA9FF085FA1FAD227DD" blockId="10.[151,1437,1513,1756]" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FF085FA1FEC3274A" bold="true" box="[151,372,1513,1539]" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Revised diagnosis.</emphasis>
Males of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FE735FA1FDCF274A" authorityName="Galiano" authorityYear="1988" box="[492,632,1513,1539]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Admesturius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FE735FA1FDCF274A" box="[492,632,1513,1539]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Admesturius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differ from those of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FCF15FA2FC6F274D" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1901" box="[878,984,1514,1540]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Scoturius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FCF15FA2FC6F274D" box="[878,984,1514,1540]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Scoturius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FB8C5FA2FBC0274A" authorityName="Ruiz &amp; Maddison" authorityYear="2015" box="[1043,1143,1514,1539]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Urupuyu" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FB8C5FA2FBC0274A" box="[1043,1143,1514,1539]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Urupuyu</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by having a single-lobed RTA, and from those of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FE2C5C46FDB6276E" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1901" box="[435,513,1550,1575]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Hurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FE2C5C46FDB6276E" box="[435,513,1550,1575]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Hurius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FD8E5C45FDCF276E" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1901" box="[529,632,1549,1575]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Atelurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FD8E5C45FDCF276E" box="[529,632,1549,1575]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Atelurius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FD175C46FCBF2761" authorityName="Galiano" authorityYear="1988" box="[648,776,1550,1576]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Simonurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FD175C46FCBF2761" box="[648,776,1550,1576]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Simonurius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FCD55C46FC0F2761" authorityName="Marta, Bustamante, Ruiz &amp; Rodrigues" authorityYear="2022" box="[842,952,1550,1576]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Guriurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FCD55C46FC0F2761" box="[842,952,1550,1576]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Guriurius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by having a curved RvTA, not projecting retrolaterally and longer than the RTA. Females of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FD4E5C79FCEA2702" authorityName="Galiano" authorityYear="1988" box="[721,861,1585,1611]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Admesturius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FD4E5C79FCEA2702" box="[721,861,1585,1611]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Admesturius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
differ from those of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FBD95C7AFB072705" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1901" box="[1094,1200,1586,1612]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Scoturius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FBD95C7AFB072705" box="[1094,1200,1586,1612]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Scoturius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FB225C79FA932702" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1901" box="[1213,1316,1585,1611]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Atelurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FB225C79FA932702" box="[1213,1316,1585,1611]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Atelurius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FAAD5C7AFA212702" authorityName="Ruiz &amp; Maddison" authorityYear="2015" box="[1330,1430,1586,1611]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Urupuyu" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FAAD5C7AFA212702" box="[1330,1430,1586,1611]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Urupuyu</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FF085C1EFEA02739" authorityName="Galiano" authorityYear="1988" box="[151,279,1622,1648]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Simonurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FF085C1EFEA02739" box="[151,279,1622,1648]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Simonurius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FED05C1EFE0A2739" authorityName="Marta, Bustamante, Ruiz &amp; Rodrigues" authorityYear="2022" box="[335,445,1622,1648]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Guriurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FED05C1EFE0A2739" box="[335,445,1622,1648]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Guriurius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by not having the copulatory openings forming an atrium, and from those of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E3574DFFA9FAB45C1EFACE2726" authorityName="Simon" authorityYear="1901" box="[1323,1401,1622,1647]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Hurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="10" pageNumber="441" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B97DE572574DFFA9FAB45C1EFACE2726" box="[1323,1401,1622,1647]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="441">Hurius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by not having separate coupling pockets. Males and females differ from other huriines by having a low carapace.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
